ed;\">做得公共交通工具司機來維生嘅<br />\n十個九個都賤種來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n想出位唔係咁</blockquote><br />\n飛機算唔算交通工"},{"pid":"8628c11dbd0aae38acb8f80b9c548b83cdc043b4","tid":412614,"uid":60492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:20:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>司機恰眼瞓可以好多原因，但係依件事令人留意到巴士司機工時長，休息少，都係事實。 講真，一口氣揸咁多個鐘真係幾辛苦，就算辛苦如中港櫃佬，埋廠裝拆貨都可以恰下，但巴士司機真係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過左排又咪係維持現狀<br />\n死又唔係死你地嘅人<br />\n香港人係咁架啦<br />\n除非keep住多幾單就有少少幫助"},{"pid":"c6ff6a966a3a06c89e51b0245fc77d7ef1d1cd87","tid":412614,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:25:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>司機恰眼瞓可以好多原因，但係依件事令人留意到巴士司機工時長，休息少，都係事實。 講真，一口氣揸咁多個鐘真係幾辛苦，就算辛苦如中港櫃佬，埋廠裝拆貨都可以恰下，但巴士司機真係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過左排又咪係維持現狀<br />\n死又唔係死你地嘅人<br />\n香港人係咁架啦<br />\n除非keep住多幾單就有少少幫助</blockquote><br />\n之後咪又係個別事件唔評論。<br />\n香港學生夠Keep住死啦，咁對香港教育制度有「少少幫助」未?"},{"pid":"f80ff08c9560ed65e026a2beb03715f4e726512f","tid":412614,"uid":111253,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恰眼訓返工即係巴士公司問題</blockquote><br />\n咁又武斷左d, 如果個車長尋晚睇完波/夜蒲完唔夠訓呢?"},{"pid":"29a618c86740537822623d7fb893c1cacff13ebb","tid":412614,"uid":12712,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:30:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做得公共交通工具司機來維生嘅<br />\n十個九個都賤種來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n想出位唔係咁</blockquote><br />\n講呢D野既人都係賤種</blockquote><br />\n呢啲人享受人地既服務就以為自己高人一等，其實最賤係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a721d3de1f00418b35111c74e1824a2d8caaea","tid":412614,"uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>恰眼訓返工即係巴士公司問題</blockquote><br />\n咁又武斷左d, 如果個車長尋晚睇完波/夜蒲完唔夠訓呢?</blockquote><br />\n屌你咪撚咁涼薄<br />\n揸1x幾個鐘，仲踩2日<br />\n用下你個死人腦都知員工唔夠時間休息啦"},{"pid":"b86dd8508228d4d8b2dd2d1cd96973efe09284e7","tid":412614,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93641925cc143977f9a0c2f10b351099eec97a6e","tid":412614,"uid":24455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:50:02.000Z","msg":"死人至再討論工時問題<br />\n公司高層根本垃圾"},{"pid":"6657ca0b3b99659cceef0950a710245aef2876d4","tid":412614,"uid":103346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:52:16.000Z","msg":"之前個啲途人行出馬路比車撞既case <br />\n個啲司機先抵幫<br />\n<br />\n呢單野，理得佢係唔係編更問題定點<br />\n始終都係撞死人<br />\n點都係抵撚死"},{"pid":"bf9ff506eceea5e7a511a9a372c2c8c4ac485b83","tid":412614,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:57:16.000Z","msg":"都話左唔夠瞓會出事架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54787f6b01f9e96fd3282441e7fd097c162798c","tid":412614,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6個鐘 30分鐘休息(連飯鐘)<br />\n真係當員工係人?</blockquote><br />\n乜服務業有人？</blockquote><br />\n3萬一個月你做唔做？"},{"pid":"be02f23b8799eb788267d8a4d043483a54014ff3","tid":412614,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"之前仲以為司機預左同的士佬沖黃燈<br />\n原來係直頭沖紅燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780771d1c8da8a5595c493863d5630453b56f7f1","tid":412614,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:19:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今朝坐巴士冇曬位, 得最後一個位就後前後左手面, 坐落都驚驚地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要死點都係死<br />\n根本冇一個位係比較安全<br />\n如果有架拖頭收唔切制撞左落巴士尾度, 坐後面果d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a634c607be20ebb8d048be10826f1a4a7a7d8ce","tid":412614,"uid":60492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>6個鐘 30分鐘休息(連飯鐘)<br />\n真係當員工係人?</blockquote><br />\n乜服務業有人？</blockquote><br />\n3萬一個月你做唔做？</blockquote><br />\n成個服務業都有問題<br />\n咩都就晒個客唔講道理<br />\n多數服務業工時長<br />\n人工再高都補唔到精神壓力啦"},{"pid":"3ce082ac5be1a89110b456410284dca10712812f","tid":412614,"uid":6136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:20:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>恰眼訓返工即係巴士公司問題</blockquote><br />\n咁又武斷左d, 如果個車長尋晚睇完波/夜蒲完唔夠訓呢?</blockquote><br />\n肇事車長上一更「通宵更」昨晨六時四十五分收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e96b7183ba06370f93272ebc8f9e37638e2d2ca","tid":412614,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死人至再討論工時問題<br />\n公司高層根本垃圾</blockquote><br />\n香港不嬲都行治療勝於預防<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf54a4fe7190669aa7a55d5db794040f512dbe6","tid":412614,"uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"屌佢其實早夜更都on撚鳩啦<br />\n一個月轉一次更<br />\n一個月早一個月夜<br />\n個人亂哂龍"},{"pid":"5edfab21a30ff1fdfd87c84df4641812ec47d3d4","tid":412614,"uid":48221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:28:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做得公共交通工具司機來維生嘅<br />\n十個九個都賤種來<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n位係咁上？"},{"pid":"981eb4420c600d6ef23e1834bc317f59ba26816f","tid":412614,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:35:47.000Z","msg":"之前唔係話果程車係個司機當日嘅第一轉車咩<br />\n<br />\n如果係就即係司機問題"},{"pid":"e49eacca6390c77443850aa1a5c43fb070bb3025","tid":412614,"uid":63414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌佢其實早夜更都on撚鳩啦<br />\n一個月轉一次更<br />\n一個月早一個月夜<br />\n個人亂哂龍</blockquote><br />\n咁既話月頭月尾唔係會好辛苦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a47a29e0f14a92378c58d257feae9f06b5a5c1","tid":412614,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:46:30.000Z","msg":"揸車撞死人判好輕我記得<br />\n呢單唔知點計"},{"pid":"79052141de80dd5b96d61572416715cafae265a8","tid":412614,"uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:56:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌佢其實早夜更都on撚鳩啦<br />\n一個月轉一次更<br />\n一個月早一個月夜<br />\n個人亂哂龍</blockquote><br />\n咁既話月頭月尾唔係會好辛苦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n辛苦到閪咁啦<br />\n我老豆咪揸九巴囉<br />\n佢轉更前一日會俾你放假<br />\n但你個日成個人會錯撚哂<br />\n訓又唔敢訓"},{"pid":"576081427e47c2dc6730f3749e2efb3d9c5581c7","tid":412614,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:59:19.000Z","msg":"嗰司機要追更，話就話中間相隔10小時。<br />\n<br />\n但你放工搭車翻屋企都要時間，沖涼搞下其他都冇左2個鐘，即刻訓，你都要預返時間起身擦牙搭車。<br />\n<br />\n所謂的10小時其實係呃人。"},{"pid":"078aaf70d353c5eb9e7e6b60b7544fa03d68ab71","tid":412614,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8692525aa264c6dbe397d651722bcf5014087d91","tid":412614,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>恰眼訓返工即係巴士公司問題</blockquote><br />\n咁又武斷左d, 如果個車長尋晚睇完波/夜蒲完唔夠訓呢?</blockquote><br />\n屌你咪撚咁涼薄<br />\n揸1x幾個鐘，仲踩2日<br />\n用下你個死人腦都知員工唔夠時間休息啦</blockquote><br />\n尋晚你老母咩，人地朝早先收工呀"},{"pid":"fe8fa52181233838df8a497e99971868bcc224bf","tid":412614,"uid":47500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:12:11.